cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.RO, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with depth sensing from a single-shot image of a monocular camera using deep learning techniques. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a deep deaberration network with a self-attention mechanism to efficiently learn the lens aberration. 
3. cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category as the paper deals with color-coded aperture (CCA) methods for measuring the depth of a scene. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is also possible as the paper mentions the proposed method providing an error-free depth map at close range, which could be useful for robotics applications. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with image processing techniques for depth sensing.
